text: Much is a municipality in Rhein-Sieg in North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. It is about 30 km northeast of Bonn and 20 km southwest of Gummersbach. == Twin towns == * Doullens, France, since 1976 * Groß Köris, Brandenburg, since 1991 == References == == Other websites == * Category:Rhein-Sieg Rural District
